{"tid":648149,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"勝色の甲－日本國家隊 JFA 與 adidas 推出別注球衣套裝","createTime":"2018-04-30T12:15:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T12:41:58.000Z","uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4c38f96585a68273ef9754842a61892e87e0525c","tid":648149,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T12:15:24.000Z","msg":"包裝盒是能摺成日本武士頭盔。<br />\n<br />\n四年一度的世界盃尚餘 45 天便會在俄羅斯舉行，賽程整體時間上都很適合大家觀看，各位又鍾情哪一隊呢？若然是捧日本隊的，那麼他們今屆所推出的球衣便不得不入手了。大家都知道日本隊的球迷是十分團結及有自律性，其精神值得我們敬佩。而 adidas 除了是專屬為 JFA 推出球衣外，是次便以限量 10,000 盒之名，推出特別包裝的球衣套裝「KACHIIRO ARMOR LIMITED PACK」，其包裝盒是可以拆下來，組裝成一個日本武士頭盔，讓大家可以戴着它來為日本隊打氣，創意度可以說是滿分。有關這套別注包裝已經能夠在網上如 ZOZOTOWN，樂天及 Yahoo 等入手，大人版本售價為 9,709 日元，而小童版本則是 7,549 日元，各位球迷不妨入手去更投入觀看賽事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hypebeast.imgix.net/https%3A%2F%2Fhk.hypebeast.com%2Ffiles%2F2018%2F04%2Fadidas-jfa-kachiiro-armor-limited-pack-1.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat&amp;fit=clip&amp;ixlib=php-1.1.0&amp;q=70&amp;w=640&amp;s=4562bd98a8c1863c7aecb6597966d75c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.imgix.net%2Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fhk.hypebeast.com%252Ffiles%252F2018%252F04%252Fadidas-jfa-kachiiro-armor-limited-pack-1.jpg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%252Cformat%26fit%3Dclip%26ixlib%3Dphp-1.1.0%26q%3D70%26w%3D640%26s%3D4562bd98a8c1863c7aecb6597966d75c&h=b57f8772&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://hypebeast.imgix.net/https%3A%2F%2Fhk.hypebeast.com%2Ffiles%2F2018%2F04%2Fadidas-jfa-kachiiro-armor-limited-pack-2.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat&amp;fit=clip&amp;ixlib=php-1.1.0&amp;q=70&amp;w=640&amp;s=70109d7ea2d0fb3dfab41ab0298aee16\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.imgix.net%2Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fhk.hypebeast.com%252Ffiles%252F2018%252F04%252Fadidas-jfa-kachiiro-armor-limited-pack-2.jpg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%252Cformat%26fit%3Dclip%26ixlib%3Dphp-1.1.0%26q%3D70%26w%3D640%26s%3D70109d7ea2d0fb3dfab41ab0298aee16&h=6e2b532c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://hypebeast.imgix.net/https%3A%2